# Dev Server

- The dev server runs on `http://localhost:3000`. NEVER run multiple instances.
- If port 3000 is not responding: first ensure your Neon branch is set up in `.env` (see neon-branching rule), then you MAY start the dev server with `pnpm dev`.
- NEVER use alternative ports (3001, 3002, etc.). Only access the app on port 3000.
